    "body": "Hello @prspace,\n\nYou can pass them when instantiating instantsearch, using the `searchParameters` options\n\n``` javascript\nvar search = instantsearch({\n    [...],\n    searchParameters: {\n        hitsPerPage: 5,\n        // Any other Algolia options\n    }\n});\n```\n",
