    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can you try doing something like this:\n\n``` js\nvar search = instantsearch({\n    // other options\n    searchParameters: {\n        facets: ['listing.status'],\n        facetsRefinements: {'listing.status': 'ACTIVE'}\n    }\n});\n```\n\nWhere \"listing.status\" is an attribute in your records and is defined as an \"Attribute for faceting\" in the dashboard.\n\nLet us know how it goes.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-01-14T09:21:42Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/752#issuecomment-171583155",
